Spain Socialists Will Increase Tax Receipts to Finance Health

-- B y   A n g e l i n e   B e n o i t
-- 
2011-10-01T10:27:31Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-10-01/spain-socialists-will-increase-tax-receipts-to-finance-health.html
Alfredo Perez Rubalcaba, the
Socialists’ candidate for  Spain ’s Nov. 20 general election, said
his party would increase taxes on tobacco and alcohol to finance
health care.  Rubalcaba spoke today during a three-day party conference
in  Madrid .  To contact the reporter on this story:
